            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I feel like 'comments' option should be empty by default. And should be set of per filetype basis. Because what is considered comment is purely filetype specific thing. There isn't really a general comment format. Also, in lots of ftplugins this is already set. We can look at where it's not set and see if any specific value makes sense for that filetype.",
